text: J.A.K.Q. Dengekitai is a Japanese television series. It is the 2nd in Toei's Super Sentai series. It was aired from April 9, 1977 to December 24, 1977. It was created by Shotaro Ishinomori, and was screened for 35 episodes. It marks the first appearance of a White Ranger in the franchise. ==Cast== * Goro Sakurai / Spade Ace: Yoshitaka Tamba * Ryu Higashi / Dia Jack: Shichiro Gou * Karen Mizuki / Heart Queen: Mitchi Love * Bunta Daichi / Clover King: Yuusuke Kazato * Sokichi Banba / Big One: Hiroshi Miyauchi ==Guest cast== * Katsuya Nakayama (9): Hiroyuki Sanada ==Songs== ; Opening theme * "J.A.K.Q.
